    "title": "Supply Chain Manager - Ashok Leyland - Top MNC",
    "description": "Ashok Leyland invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Supply Chain Manager at our Kanpur location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Ashok Leyland:\nAshok Leyland is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kanpur, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Ashok Leyland!",
